{"tid":1075823,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"12歲女童元朗家中上吊亡","createTime":"2019-03-24T12:05:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-24T17:13:40.000Z","uid":160807,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6be4cbc96ed0243cc8098769a16485af3f7f2f4d","tid":1075823,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"12歲女童元朗家中上吊亡<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，警方接獲一名男子報案，指其12歲女兒在元朗朗景臺的寓所睡房內，以繩上吊，他慌忙將女兒解下，惟已陷昏迷，救護員趕抵將她送院，可惜搶救不治。警方於現場沒有撿獲遺書，初步調查相信事件沒有可疑，死因有待驗屍後確定。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59404472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59404472&d=6SPFYKHnGSG2Q49qavPU8olFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=16a2fc0a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190323%2F59404472&h=e2c0edad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190323/59404472</a><br />\n<br />\n小學生已經咁大壓力咁唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fecf46431a03480a534ef90219d981b2c32d24e6","tid":1075823,"uid":160807,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:25:34.000Z","msg":"香港讀書壓力實在太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b180c3af5a01bdf360f626a046a5de2606dda43f","tid":1075823,"uid":192491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc53eae274462263de253b8bb69c9e614f292d9f","tid":1075823,"uid":75211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:26:53.000Z","msg":"咁細個吊臘鴨"},{"pid":"da107760c4f7238a0375900089b388aa0c3b27e0","tid":1075823,"uid":177338,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"